<script>
    function updateImage() {
        var videoFrame = document.getElementById('videoFrame');
        var overlay = document.getElementById('overlay');

        // Adjust the size and position of the overlay to match the video frame
        overlay.style.width = videoFrame.offsetWidth + 'px';
        overlay.style.height = videoFrame.offsetHeight + 'px';

        var image = new Image();
        image.src = 'http://192.168.1.110:81/stream?' + new Date().getTime(); // Append a timestamp to force video refresh
        image.onload = function () {
            videoFrame.contentWindow.location.reload(); // Reload the iframe to update the video
        };
    }

    setInterval(updateImage, 1000); // Update video every 1 second (1000 milliseconds)
</script>
